Nigeria international and Arsenal forward, Alex Iwobi has made a debut in his first film role in the soon to be released film, Inpadisu. The film, now trending on social media, features Iwobi being pursued all over the place, apparently because of choices he made in the film. Iwobi also took to his Instagram page @Alexanderiwobi to confirm his role in the film alongside award-winning actress, Somkele Iyamah. He shared the thriller and wrote: “Shot my Nollywood debut last month. A movie about choices coming soon.”   Shot My Nollywood Debut Last Month ‍. A Movie About ‘Choices’ Coming Soon … #INPADISU A post shared by  Alexander Iwobi (@alexanderiwobi) on Aug 17, 2018 at 4:58am PDT  **NAN